multiflexi-housekeeper (1.0.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Initial release — 8 housekeeping duties:
    StaleTaskFinalization, OrphanedJobCleanup, ScheduleIntegrity,
    DataRetentionCleanup, DiskTempFileCleanup, LogPruning,
    RuntemplateCounterRecalc, CredentialHealthCheck.
  * Runs as systemd timer (hourly, Persistent=true) or long-running daemon.
  * Supports --dry-run mode and MULTIFLEXI_HOUSEKEEPER_SKIP_DUTIES.

